;#10;&amp;#10;ooo Mugen no Ken (Ki, Attack)&amp;#10;The Shinobi makes two consecutive attacks against the same target.&amp;#10;oooo Hakai Shinken (Ki, Charge)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;+ 4 Attack.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
